title: The Taylor Swift Deepfakes Disaster Threatens to Change the Internet As We Know It
description: Deepfakes and AI-generated nonconsensual sexual imagery have been a problem for a long time. But with the resurgence of attention on them, we're facing a reckoning.

title: Man Who Sued 'Are We Dating the Same Guy?' Groups Files Class Action Lawsuit
description: Nikko D'Ambrosio of Illinois had his first case dismissed, and refiled as a class action that seeks other guys who feel harmed by "red flags or tea?" dating groups.

title: Binance Code and Internal Passwords Exposed on GitHub for Months
description: A takedown request said the GitHub account was “hosting and distributing leaks of internal code which poses significant risk to BINANCE.”
